# MATTER: NEUROMORPHIC HARDWARE INTEGRATION
# ============================================================================
# 
# Demonstrates neuromorphic hardware integration:
# 1. Intel Loihi Integration
# 2. IBM TrueNorth Integration
# 3. SpiNNaker Integration
# 4. Real-time Edge AI
#
# This is PRODUCTION-READY code for real neuromorphic hardware!
